    "description": "Discipline: Neigong\nSkill: Empathy TN 6\nType: Normal\nQi: 6\n\nYou erase the barriers in your mind separating you from nature, and form a link with all flower and leaf bearing plants in the area, causing them to unleash a powerful hail of deadly petals. The petals are light but become hard and sharp as steel. On a Success, you cause a 10-foot swath of petals per Rank of Qi to sweep before you for up to 150 feet, doing 2d10 Damage per Rank of Neigong to all affected targets. Cathartic: The area increases to a 50-foot swath per Rank of Qi and Damage becomes Open.",
